@page "/learn"
@layout LearnLayout

<div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="font-accent"><span class="text-accent">DaisiBot</span> Mastery Course</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted mt-3" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
        A hands-on course that takes you from zero to confidently running your own
        decentralized AI assistant &mdash; across terminal, desktop, mobile, and web.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="glass-card mb-4">
    <h4 class="font-accent text-accent">How This Course Works</h4>
    <p>
        Each module builds on the previous one using evidence-based learning techniques:
        <strong>scaffolded progression</strong> (simple &rarr; complex),
        <strong>active recall checkpoints</strong> (quiz yourself at the end of every module), and
        <strong>concrete examples</strong> tied to real DaisiBot workflows.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-0">
        Work through the modules in order. By the end you will be able to run local inference,
        manage conversations with multiple think levels, install and create skills, deploy
        autonomous bots, and keep everything secure.
    </p>
</div>

<h3 class="font-accent mb-3">Modules</h3>

<div class="row g-3">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/architecture" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">1 &middot; Architecture &amp; Core Concepts</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">What DaisiBot is, how the DAISI network works, and the mental model you need before touching any config.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/installation" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">2 &middot; Prerequisites &amp; Installation</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">System requirements, building from source, and what happens on first launch.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/configuration" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">3 &middot; Configuration &amp; Host Mode</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">User settings, host mode vs. DaisiNet, model management, and ORC connection.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/conversations" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">4 &middot; Conversations &amp; Chat</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Think levels, streaming responses, slash commands, and chat statistics.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/skills" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">5 &middot; Skills &amp; Marketplace</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Browsing, installing, creating, and publishing AI skills.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/bots" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">6 &middot; Bots &amp; Automation</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Autonomous agents that plan, execute, and report back on a schedule.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/security" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">7 &middot; Security Best Practices</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Authentication, tool permissions, skill review, and protecting your keys.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="/learn/next-steps" class="text-decoration-none">
            <div class="glass-card h-100">
                <h5 class="font-accent text-accent">8 &middot; Next Steps &amp; Roadmap</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Recommended features, community contributions, and where the project is heading.</p>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
